<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Since then, various <a href=3D"https://link.ma=
il.bloombergbusiness.com/click/35861449.260284/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGF4cG9saWN5=
Y2VudGVyLm9yZy90YXh2b3gvdGF4LWdpbW1pY2stYm94eA/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBbf9=
23042" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" sty=
le=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width=
: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background=
-color: #ccc;">tax experts</a> and <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbu=
siness.com/click/35861449.260284/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW=
9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDMtMTMvc2F2ZS10YXhlcy13aXRoLWJveHgtaXQtaXMtdG9vLWdvb=
2QtdG8tYmUtdHJ1ZT9jbXBpZD1CQkQwNjI3MjRfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWls=
JnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yNDA2MjcmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV=
5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB2ca46ede" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscop=
e=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration:=
 none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; b=
order-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Bloomberg Opinion colum=
nists</a> have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/358=
61449.260284/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMj=
